Bounce is 2D 'game' based on Microsoft's XNA framework.
It utilizes the Farseer physics engine.

The goal of this project is to create a physics playground in which I can simulate theoretical physical scenarios.

Controls:

BrickBreaker Movement: Arrow keys.
Spacebar will launch or reset the ball.
Enter will push a new game onto the stack.
Delete will pop a game off the stack.

Camera Movement: Numpad arrow keys.
Numpad 5 to reset zoom and rotation.
Page up / page down to rotate the camera
